uring retrieval.\n\nSo I'm marking this as needing improvement—the hints_missing finding has real impact. For why it persisted: the fabrication finding was likely a false positive since the RST source actually supports that annotation, so Phase E correctly kept it. The hints_missing issue remained because BatchAction wasn't added to s3 hints despite being relevant to the flow details there.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":29921,"cache_read_input_tokens":29836,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":29921,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"57765aa8-d154-41a6-85cd-aa94020a7987","uuid":"7a39ebf3-edce-49b2-9159-d5b9ff9b4e7f"}
